    "body": "Reopen https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm/pull/15117 and https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm/pull/15126 as one completed PR here. \n\nHi~, we are the tech team from vipshop.com and mainly use vLLM in our production deployment. This PR is mainly focused on optimizing DeepSeek-R1 671B inference performance on NVIDIA L20 devices using vLLM with pp3 + tp8. We hope that this PR will further enhance the performance of vLLM on NVIDIA L20. This PR has the following contributions:\n\n- 1. Tuned fused MoE and w8a8 block fp8 performance on NVIDIA L20\n\nAdded tuned w8a8 and fused MoE configurations for NVIDIA L20, which can boost the decode throughput of DeepSeek-R1 671B with pp3 + tp8 by up to `10~15%`.\n\n- 2. Add w8a8 block fp8 tuning script \n\nAdapted from https://github.com/sgl-project/sglang/blob/main/benchmark/kernels/quantization/tuning_block_wise_kernel.py.\n\n```bash\n# Tune triton w8a8 block fp8 for DeepSeek-V3/DeepSeek-R1:\npython3 benchmark_w8a8_block_fp8.py --tp-size 8 --input-type fp8\n# Then copy then configs to vllm/model_executor/layers/quantization/utils/configs\n```\n\nBefore this PR:  \n\n```bash\nWARNING 03-19 15:21:07 [fp8_utils.py:431] Using default W8A8 Block FP8 kernel config. Performance might be sub-optimal! Config file not found at /usr/local/lib/python3.10/dist-packages/vllm/model_executor/layers/quantization/utils/configs/N=1536,K=7168,device_name=NVIDIA_L20,dtype=fp8_w8a8,block_shape=[128,128].json\n........\nWARNING 03-19 15:21:08 [fused_moe.py:874] Using default MoE config. Performance might be sub-optimal! Config file not found at /usr/local/lib/python3.10/site-packages/vllm/model_executor/layers/fused_moe/configs/E=256,N=256,device_name=NVIDIA_L20,dtype=fp8_w8a8,block_shape=[128,128].json\n\n```\n\nAfter this PR:\n\n```bash\nINFO 03-22 12:10:07 [fp8_utils.py:422] Using configuration from /usr/local/lib/python3.10/dist-packages/vllm/model_executor/layers/quantization/utils/configs/N=1536,K=7168,device_name=NVIDIA_L20,dtype=fp8_w8a8,block_shape=[128,128].json for W8A8 Block FP8 kernel.\nINFO 03-22 12:10:07 [fp8_utils.py:422] Using configuration from /usr/local/lib/python3.10/dist-packages/vllm/model_executor/layers/quantization/utils/configs/N=576,K=7168,device_name=NVIDIA_L20,dtype=fp8_w8a8,block_shape=[128,128].json for W8A8 Block FP8 kernel.\nINFO 03-22 12:10:07 [fp8_utils.py:422] Using configuration from /usr/local/lib/python3.10/dist-packages/vllm/model_executor/layers/quantization/utils/configs/N=3072,K=1536,device_name=NVIDIA_L20,dtype=fp8_w8a8,block_shape=[128,128].json for W8A8 Block FP8 kernel.\nINFO 03-22 12:10:07 [fp8_utils.py:422] Using configuration from /usr/local/lib/python3.10/dist-packages/vllm/model_executor/layers/quantization/utils/configs/N=7168,K=2048,device_name=NVIDIA_L20,dtype=fp8_w8a8,block_shape=[128,128].json for W8A8 Block FP8 kernel.\nINFO 03-22 12:10:07 [fp8_utils.py:422] Using configuration from /usr/local/lib/python3.10/dist-packages/vllm/model_executor/layers/quantization/utils/configs/N=4608,K=7168,device_name=NVIDIA_L20,dtype=fp8_w8a8,block_shape=[128,128].json for W8A8 Block FP8 kernel.\nINFO 03-22 12:10:07 [fp8_utils.py:422] Using configuration from /usr/local/lib/python3.10/dist-packages/vllm/model_executor/layers/quantization/utils/configs/N=7168,K=2304,device_name=NVIDIA_L20,dtype=fp8_w8a8,block_shape=[128,128].json for W8A8 Block FP8 kernel.\nINFO 03-22 12:10:07 [fp8_utils.py:422] Using configuration from /usr/local/lib/python3.10/dist-packages/vllm/model_executor/layers/quantization/utils/configs/N=512,K=7168,device_name=NVIDIA_L20,dtype=fp8_w8a8,block_shape=[128,128].json for W8A8 Block FP8 kernel.\nINFO 03-22 12:10:07 [fp8_utils.py:422] Using configuration from /usr/local/lib/python3.10/dist-packages/vllm/model_executor/layers/quantization/utils/configs/N=7168,K=256,device_name=NVIDIA_L20,dtype=fp8_w8a8,block_shape=[128,128].json for W8A8 Block FP8 kernel.\nINFO 03-22 12:10:08 [fused_moe.py:874] Using configuration from /usr/local/lib/python3.10/dist-packages/vllm/model_executor/layers/fused_moe/configs/E=256,N=256,device_name=NVIDIA_L20,dtype=fp8_w8a8,block_shape=[128,128].json for MoE layer.\n```\n\nPerformance 4K input & 1K output:\n\n```bash\n#### command\npython3 benchmark_serving.py \\\n        --backend vllm \\\n        --model /workspace/DeepSeek-R1 \\\n        --port 8862 \\\n        --endpoint /v1/completions \\\n        --dataset-name random \\\n        --dataset-path ${SHAREGPT_DATASET_PATH} \\\n        --random-input-len 4096 \\\n        --random-output-len 1024 \\\n        --random-prefix-len 0 \\\n        --ignore-eos \\\n        --max-concurrency 16 \\\n        --num-prompts 16\n\n#### Before\n# 131.55 TPS with concurrency 16, 4K input & 1K output, TTFT 8749ms\nMaximum request concurrency: 16\n============ Serving Benchmark Result ============\nSuccessful requests:                     16\nBenchmark duration (s):                  124.74\nTotal input tokens:                      65536\nTotal generated tokens:                  16384\nRequest throughput (req/s):              0.13\nOutput token throughput (tok/s):         131.35\nTotal Token throughput (tok/s):          656.75\n---------------Time to First Token----------------\nMean TTFT (ms):                          8749.86\nMedian TTFT (ms):                        9009.79\nP99 TTFT (ms):                           13242.30\n-----Time per Output Token (excl. 1st token)------\nMean TPOT (ms):                          112.99\nMedian TPOT (ms):                        112.77\nP99 TPOT (ms):                           117.74\n---------------Inter-token Latency----------------\nMean ITL (ms):                           112.99\nMedian ITL (ms):                         108.20\nP99 ITL (ms):                            123.80\n==================================================\n\n#### After \n# 145.91 TPS with concurrency 16, 4K input & 1K output, TTFT 8155ms\nMaximum request concurrency: 16\n============ Serving Benchmark Result ============\nSuccessful requests:                     16\nBenchmark duration (s):                  112.29\nTotal input tokens:                      65536\nTotal generated tokens:                  16384\nRequest throughput (req/s):              0.14\nOutput token throughput (tok/s):         145.91\nTotal Token throughput (tok/s):          729.54\n---------------Time to First Token----------------\nMean TTFT (ms):                          8155.07\nMedian TTFT (ms):                        8429.93\nP99 TTFT (ms):                           12540.61\n-----Time per Output Token (excl. 1st token)------\nMean TPOT (ms):                          101.42\nMedian TPOT (ms):                        101.19\nP99 TPOT (ms):                           106.09\n---------------Inter-token Latency----------------\nMean ITL (ms):                           101.42\nMedian ITL (ms):                         96.11\nP99 ITL (ms):                            113.22\n==================================================\n```\n \nPerformance 1K input & 4K output\n\n```bash\n#### command\npython3 benchmark_serving.py \\\n        --backend vllm \\\n        --model /workspace/DeepSeek-R1 \\\n        --port 8862 \\\n        --endpoint /v1/completions \\\n        --dataset-name random \\\n        --dataset-path ${SHAREGPT_DATASET_PATH} \\\n        --random-input-len 1024 \\\n        --random-output-len 4096 \\\n        --random-prefix-len 0 \\\n        --ignore-eos \\\n        --max-concurrency 32 \\\n        --num-prompts 32\n\n#### Before\n# 250.71 TPS with concurrency 32, 1K input & 4K output, TTFT 4367ms\nMaximum request concurrency: 32\n============ Serving Benchmark Result ============\nSuccessful requests:                     32\nBenchmark duration (s):                  522.81\nTotal input tokens:                      32768\nTotal generated tokens:                  131072\nRequest throughput (req/s):              0.06\nOutput token throughput (tok/s):         250.71\nTotal Token throughput (tok/s):          313.39\n---------------Time to First Token----------------\nMean TTFT (ms):                          4367.81\nMedian TTFT (ms):                        4440.48\nP99 TTFT (ms):                           6910.16\n-----Time per Output Token (excl. 1st token)------\nMean TPOT (ms):                          126.53\nMedian TPOT (ms):                        126.51\nP99 TPOT (ms):                           127.27\n---------------Inter-token Latency----------------\nMean ITL (ms):                           126.53\nMedian ITL (ms):                         125.66\nP99 ITL (ms):                            145.68\n==================================================\n\n#### After\n# 295.71 TPS with concurrency 32, 1K input & 4K output, TTFT 4152.47ms\nMaximum request concurrency: 32\n============ Serving Benchmark Result ============\nSuccessful requests:                     32\nBenchmark duration (s):                  443.24\nTotal input tokens:                      32768\nTotal generated tokens:                  131072\nRequest throughput (req/s):              0.07\nOutput token throughput (tok/s):         295.71\nTotal Token throughput (tok/s):          369.64\n---------------Time to First Token----------------\nMean TTFT (ms):                          4152.47\nMedian TTFT (ms):                        4207.50\nP99 TTFT (ms):                           6710.61\n-----Time per Output Token (excl. 1st token)------\nMean TPOT (ms):                          107.16\nMedian TPOT (ms):                        107.15\nP99 TPOT (ms):                           107.88\n---------------Inter-token Latency----------------\nMean ITL (ms):                           107.16\nMedian ITL (ms):                         106.29\nP99 ITL (ms):                            125.92\n==================================================\n```\n",
